'''朗納·德瑞福'''（{{lang_en|Ronald Drever}}，{{bd|1931年|10月26日|2017年|3月7日|catIdx=Drever}}），男，[[英國|英國]]實驗物理學者，[[加州理工學院|加州理工學院]]榮譽教授，是[[LIGO|LIGO]]計畫創始人之一。德瑞福是能夠穩定激光的{{le|龐德-德瑞福-霍爾技術|Pound-Drever-Hall technique}}的發明者之一。對於2015年9月人類首次直接探測到引力波的創舉，這技術具有關鍵性作用。<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite web | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/science/12153127/British-scientist-who-played-key-role-in-gravitational-waves-research-is-suffering-from-dementia.html | title=British scientist who played key role in gravitational waves research is suffering from dementia | publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited | work=The Telegraph | date=12 February 2016 | accessdate=12 February 2016 | author=Knapton, Sarah | archive-date=2019-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129165820/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/science/12153127/British-scientist-who-played-key-role-in-gravitational-waves-research-is-suffering-from-dementia.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PRL-20160211">{{cite journal |author=Abbott, B.P. |title=Observation of Gravitational Waves from a Binary Black Hole Merger |url=http://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102 |journal=Phys. Rev. Lett. |volume=116 |pages=061102 |year=2016 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102 |display-authors=etal |access-date=2016-05-04 |archive-date=2019-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025233058/https://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.116.061102 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Nature_11Feb16">{{cite journal |title=Einstein's gravitational waves found at last |journal=Nature News |url=http://www.nature.com/news/einstein-s-gravitational-waves-found-at-last-1.19361 |date=11 February 2016 |last=Castelvecchi |first=Davide |last2=Witze |first2=Alexandra |doi=10.1038/nature.2016.19361 |accessdate=11 February 2016 |archive-date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216095503/http://www.nature.com/news/einstein-s-gravitational-waves-found-at-last-1.19361 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
德瑞福在[[格拉斯哥大學|格拉斯哥大學]]開始了學術生涯。後來，他被聘請至加州理工學院。在那裏，他成立了一個引力波計畫。<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite web | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/science/12153127/British-scientist-who-played-key-role-in-gravitational-waves-research-is-suffering-from-dementia.html | title=British scientist who played key role in gravitational waves research is suffering from dementia | publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited | work=The Telegraph | date=12 February 2016 | accessdate=12 February 2016 | author=Knapton, Sarah}}</ref><ref name="NYT">{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/science/ligo-gravitational-waves-black-holes-einstein.html?_r=0 | title=Gravitational Waves Detected, Confirming Einstein’s Theory | publisher=The New York Times Company | work=New York Times | date=11 February 2016 | accessdate=12 February 2016 | author=OVERBYE, DENNIS , CORUM, JONATHAN  and DRAKEFORD, JASON | archive-date=2021-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316235835/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/science/ligo-gravitational-waves-black-holes-einstein.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

德瑞福后期的研究涉及到發展一種光學浮置科技，其可以使得實驗儀器與地震隔離。

退休后因痴呆症而在蘇格蘭的一家療養院休養。<ref name="Telegraph" />

2017年3月7日在苏格兰[[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]]逝去，享年85岁<ref>{{cite web|author=Jonathan Amos|title=Gravitational waves pioneer Ronald Drever dies|work=BBC news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-39212305|accessdate=2017-03-10|archive-date=2017-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310064103/http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-39212305|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 榮譽與獎勵 ==
德瑞福獲得的主要榮譽與獎勵有：
*2002年，被遴選為[[美國文理科學院|美國文理科學院]]院士。<ref>[http://media.caltech.edu/press_releases/12285 Five Caltech Faculty Members Elected to Membership in the American Academy of Arts and Sciences] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601181737/http://media.caltech.edu/press_releases/12285 |date=2010-06-01 }}</ref>
*與[[萊納·魏斯|萊納·魏斯]]共享2007年 {{le|愛因斯坦獎|Einstein Prize (APS)}}。
*由於「探測到[[GW150914|引力波的蹤跡]]，開啟天文學與物理學的新視野」，德瑞福、[[基普·索恩|基普·索恩]]、[[萊納·魏斯|萊納·魏斯]]與1012位團隊同工共同榮獲2016年[[基礎物理學突破獎|基礎物理學突破獎]]。<ref>{{cite web | url =https://breakthroughprize.org/News/32 | title =Special Breakthrough Prize In Fundamental Physics Awarded For Detection Of Gravitational Waves 100 Years After Albert Einstein Predicted Their Existence | date =2 May 2016 | publisher =Breakthrough Prize | access-date =2016-07-09 | archive-date =2016-05-07 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160507164450/https://breakthroughprize.org/News/32 | dead-url =no }}</ref>
*因為「探測到引力波」，德瑞福、索恩、魏斯獲得2016年[[格鲁伯宇宙学奖|格鲁伯宇宙学奖]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gruber.yale.edu/cosmology/press/2016-gruber-cosmology-prize-press-release |title=2016 Gruber Cosmology Prize |access-date=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2017-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171106030937/http://gruber.yale.edu/cosmology/press/2016-gruber-cosmology-prize-press-release |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*由於對「激光干涉儀重力波觀測站LIGO的構思和設計」，德瑞福、索恩、魏斯獲頒2016年邵逸夫獎。<ref>{{cite web
